---
---

<section class="dark relative overflow-hidden border-b border-white/5">
  <!-- Background grid -->
  <div class="grid-bg absolute inset-0" />
  <!-- Radial glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 h-[500px] w-[800px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-primary/8 blur-3xl" />

  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 py-32 text-center">
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-primary">
        <span class="size-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse" />
        Procesamiento distribuido en tiempo real
      </span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="animate-fade-in-up delay-100 max-w-3xl text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
      Imágenes procesadas
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary/60 bg-clip-text text-transparent">en paralelo</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="animate-fade-in-up delay-200 max-w-xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
      Sube una imagen, elige un filtro y obtén el resultado. Tu imagen se divide y procesa entre múltiples servidores automáticamente.
    </p>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up delay-300 flex items-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="/app"
        class="glow-sm inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-8 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-foreground transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:bg-primary/90"
      >
        Procesar imagen
      </a>
      <a
        href="#features"
        class="inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition-all hover:border-white/20 hover:text-foreground"
      >
        Saber más
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
